# ORIG TITLE    “Prince Regent” of mafia clan seized near Naples . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Police in Italy have arrested the son of one of the most powerful Mafia bosses in the country in a dawn raid on a bar. Carmine Schiavone was seen as the regent of the Casalesi clan after the arrest of his father in 2008. The Casalesi are the most influential of the Camorra, the organisation known informally as the Naples mafia. 
